WEBVTT

00:05.572 --> 00:07.006
<i>Urca de Lima,</i>

00:07.074 --> 00:10.009
the largest Spanish treasure galleon
in the Americas.

00:10.077 --> 00:13.212
A page was torn from the log
with the Urca's course and schedule.

00:13.280 --> 00:15.081
Take them into custody.

00:20.721 --> 00:22.154
The schedule is here
on the island.

00:22.222 --> 00:24.757
The thief who stole it
has offered to sell it to me.

00:24.825 --> 00:26.826
5,000 pesos in pearls.

00:26.894 --> 00:29.528
- After I get payment, we leave tonight.
- Leave with me.

00:29.596 --> 00:32.298
I've spent my life trying
to build something here.

00:32.366 --> 00:34.567
If you ever challenge me
again in front of my crew,

00:34.635 --> 00:36.302
I might just forget
that I loved you once.

00:36.370 --> 00:38.070
The page is gone.
Don't lie to me!

00:41.541 --> 00:43.409
- Where's the page?
- You're looking at it.

00:43.477 --> 00:46.612
I took drastic measures.
Your schedule is up here.

00:48.548 --> 00:50.583
Ah!

